      "amount": "2 tablespoons"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Grill the chestnuts for about 10 minutes, turning occasionally until they are lightly charred and crispy on the outside.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together soy sauce, gochujang, sugar, minced garlic cloves, and chopped green onions. Stir well until the sugar is fully dissolved.",
    "Drizzle oil over the grilled chestnuts to prevent sticking.",
    "Add the mixed seasoning into the bowl of grilling chestnuts and toss gently until all the ingredients are evenly coated with sauce.",
    "Serve immediately while still hot."
